dc_title_s: Map of the lower Mississippi River from the mouth of the Ohio River to the head of the passes in thirty three sheets
dc_description_s: Shows mileage, names of local geographic features and landings, land use, some landowners and plantations. Title from cover sheet. "Published in 1884 & 1900, 1895-96 & 1916 by the Mississippi River Commission, created by act of Congress, June 28, 1879."--Cover sheet. Historic Maps copy has ms. annotations on some sheets; some sheets mounted on cloth.
dc_publisher_s: [Vicksburg, Miss.] : Mississippi River Commission, 1916 (N.Y. : Snyder & Black)
